  "section_name": "Financial Analysis",
  "text": "Apple reported Q3 2025 revenue of $94,036,000,000, representing a year-over-year decline of 1.39% according to the YoY growth calculation. This compares to Q2 2025 revenue of $95,359,000,000, indicating sequential pressure on the top line. The modest revenue contraction suggests potential headwinds in key product categories or geographic markets during the quarter.",
